{
  "stem": "979.2",
  "chunk_idx": 18,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 8.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I say, always I'll ask him, and he's going to answer my prayers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Now when I was in the camp, I said please, God.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I say, I always answer my prayers-- the little things I asked you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But this-- this time, I want a very big favor.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't want to die here.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Don't let me die here and my sister.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "He says, I know you won't.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You will do it for me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then I was peaceful.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "No matter what went wrong, how horrible it was, I'm not going to die here.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And that what make me live.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because when I tell you the rest what happened, you can not believe.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I, you know-- and that when I wanted to tell you is that when we-- when we went, I was praying.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I say, when the music-- and my father-- when-- when I was a kid, when I started to have the-- the accordion lessons, he used to walk me in a tiny little room-- very little-- just for the, you know, the-- for the icebox.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "We used to have a sort of ice box-- not like here, to put-- the man used to bring the ice-- so little.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And it was enough for two persons to sit there.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he used to walk me there and made me there stay two hours to practice my accordion.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And then when I came out, I was crying.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And he says-- I was crying.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "But I had to play, because he's listening that I'm studying.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 80,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "But then when I came out, he says, you think--",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
